title: 2019 Week 4 Preview
itunes:title: 2019 Week 4 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler preview each of the Week 4 games and try to set their lock scores straight. The snake draft seems to cause problems and the heroes address their "game watching" habits.
